From: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
Date: Mon, 29 Sep 2025 12:07:51 -0700
Subject: perf map: Constify objdump offset/address conversion APIs
Git-commit: c0b8a55a1180274247f6081260cd854c2a309379
Patch-mainline: v6.18-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

Make the map argument const as the conversion act won't modify the map
and this allows other callers to use a const struct map.

Signed-off-by: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
